A clear divergence?taking the bottomish long VOP bars as reference  the yellow shaded zone traded 557m at vwap 0.027for reference  only 334m shares are in public hands and those before rights are all deep in the water as the stock collapsed from 20 cent region before the entry of Chua Wei Kee their chairman.
